          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "End of Act 2:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The Protagonist and Love Interest have grown closer and may have shared an intimate moment. The stakes reach their highest point as the romantic relationship’s importance jeopardizes the Protagonist’s chance to succeed at their stated goal—or vice versa—and their goal shifts. This is the \"Finally\" moment for readers, where they get to see the relationship begin to take a physical step forward."
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "How have the Protagonist and Love Interest deepened their relationship? This can be a physical connection, a verbal discussion, or an acceptance that this is love."
                  }
                ],
                "type": "list-item"
              },
              {
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "How does the deepening relationship conflict with the external goals of the characters?"
                  }
                ],
                "type": "list-item"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 2 makes up 50% of the story from 25% - 75%."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Swivel: Second Turning Point occurs around the 60-62% mark, three-quarters of the way through Act 2."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
