          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Middle of Act 2:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The Protagonist and Love Interest are still committed to their goals, but their growing emotions for each other begin to create conflict. A situation irrevocably binds the Protagonist with the Love Interest, often while tweaking sexual tensions. This situation alters the perspective of the Protagonist and has further implications for the outcome of the relationship. The Protagonist begins to consider a relationship but realizes that it cannot work because of their external goals or false beliefs."
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "What event glues the Protagonist and Love Interest together? This could be an illness, friends seeing each other in a new way, or an act of selflessness, seemingly contrary to the Love Interest's personality."
                  }
                ],
                "type": "list-item"
              },
              {
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Depict the Protagonist's consideration of the relationship and \"what if\" moment. How and why do they cling to their external goals and/or false beliefs?"
                  }
                ],
                "type": "list-item"
              },
              {
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Give the readers a 'this could actually work, but no' moment to increase the tension and stakes."
                  }
                ],
                "type": "list-item"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 2 makes up 50% of the story from 25% - 75%."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Midpoint/Raising the Stakes occurs around the 50% mark."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
