            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Beginning of Act 1:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "This is the opening scene or sequence identifying the Protagonist's internal and/or external conflict. It introduces the reader to the current status quo of the Protagonist with something \"wrong\" implied as the reader views their ordinary world. The Protagonist and their Love Interest have goals and desires, which will come into conflict."
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Introduce the reader to how the Protagonist functions in their ordinary life."
                  }
                ],
                "type": "list-item"
              },
              {
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Include something about their life that displeases the Protagonist or appears wrong to the reader."
                  }
                ],
                "type": "list-item"
              },
              {
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Identify the Protagonist's conflicts and goals as you develop a three-dimensional character."
                  }
                ],
                "type": "list-item"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 1 makes up the first 25% of the story."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Setup/Hook should take approximately 12-13% of the story, or the midway point of Act 1"
